{
  "id": "69a18a72f00a79f90a3d328d",
  "title": "そろばん",
  "created": 1772194422,
  "updated": 1775269198,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a18a72f00a79f90a3d328d",
      "text": "そろばん",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772194422,
      "updated": 1772194422
    },
    {
      "id": "69d069ff000000000096c083",
      "text": "漢字表記：算盤",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266304,
      "updated": 1775266323
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06a23000000000096c085",
      "text": "Abacus",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266339,
      "updated": 1775266343
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06a00000000000096c084",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266305,
      "updated": 1775266305
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18a7600000000008b6e96",
      "text": "[東洋の計算機]と言われる（[天空の城ラピュタ]など）",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772194422,
      "updated": 1772335634
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18a9d00000000008b6e99",
      "text": "\t電子計算機と比較すると「[計算機]」と呼べるほどの機能はない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772194462,
      "updated": 1772335636
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18ab500000000008b6e9a",
      "text": "\t計算過程をメモし、不要な情報を直ちに破棄することができる物理的機械（[からくり]）",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772194485,
      "updated": 1772335639
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18ae700000000008b6e9b",
      "text": "\t\t動力はない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772194535,
      "updated": 1772194546
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18af700000000008b6e9e",
      "text": "\t\t自動車に対する自転車みたいなもの",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772194551,
      "updated": 1772194563
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18b0400000000008b6e9f",
      "text": "\t\t\t動力をユーザーが与える必要がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772194565,
      "updated": 1772194579
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18eac00000000008b6ea5",
      "text": " なにか魔法みたいな事ができるわけではなく、ワーキングメモリを物理的な玉に移譲できる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772195500,
      "updated": 1772195502
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06a4d000000000096c086",
      "text": " ある意味揮発性メモリのような側面がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266381,
      "updated": 1775266400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18af300000000008b6e9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772194547,
      "updated": 1772194547
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0750a000000000096c0c8",
      "text": "筆算の場合は下の桁から順に行わなければ繰り上がりの連鎖により面倒なことになるが、そろばんの場合は下から計算しても上から計算しても良い。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775269130,
      "updated": 1775269198
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0750a000000000096c0c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775269130,
      "updated": 1775269130
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06af0000000000096c087",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/そろばん",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266544,
      "updated": 1775266545
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06af2000000000096c089",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/珠算",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266546,
      "updated": 1775266550
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06af0000000000096c088",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266544,
      "updated": 1775266544
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18af300000000008b6e9d",
      "text": "上に少数（1つか2つ）の珠があり、下に多数（4つか5つ）の珠がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772194547,
      "updated": 1775266255
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18c5400000000008b6ea0",
      "text": "\t上の珠を五珠、下の珠を一珠という。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772194901,
      "updated": 1775266585
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06b19000000000096c08a",
      "text": "\t五珠を下げると +5 を表し、一珠を上げると +1 を表す。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266585,
      "updated": 1775266625
    },
    {
      "id": "69a18ea700000000008b6ea2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772195495,
      "updated": 1772195495
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06854000000000096c07e",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a0cbe0bc26685b88adf45ffda335a7f1]][https://gyazo.com/fe3d385224d537b9821e60c3ef7b2d74]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775265876,
      "updated": 1775265942
    },
    {
      "id": "69d067f4000000000096c07d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775265780,
      "updated": 1775265780
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06764000000000096c07c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775265637,
      "updated": 1775265637
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06b4a000000000096c08b",
      "text": "[ 添入]：繰り上がりがない場合は素直に五珠を下げたり一珠を上げたりすれば良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266635,
      "updated": 1775268175
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06b80000000000096c08c",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/2cc3a85053cee307371b134e5658e608]　　　[https://gyazo.com/67244929a7f5ac16209be42500fb3227]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266688,
      "updated": 1775266964
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06c8d000000000096c08f",
      "text": "\tこの計算の際に 2+2 = 4 だなと考えるのではなく、一珠を 2 つ動かして、2 を足すことだけを考える。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266958,
      "updated": 1775267040
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06cca000000000096c090",
      "text": "\t\tワーキングメモリが少し節約される",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267019,
      "updated": 1775267029
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06c80000000000096c08e",
      "text": "\t同様に 1+6 = 7 だなと考えるのではなく、五珠と一珠を動かして 6 を足すことだけを考える。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266944,
      "updated": 1775267082
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06d24000000000096c091",
      "text": "\t暗算の際には珠を想像し、脳内の珠を読む形で答えを書く",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267108,
      "updated": 1775267145
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06d68000000000096c092",
      "text": "\t\t玉を動かす動作をするとイメージしやすいのか（そろばんができる人は）暗算中に指を動かす人が多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267177,
      "updated": 1775267232
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06e57000000000096c09a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267415,
      "updated": 1775267416
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06e57000000000096c09b",
      "text": "[開排]: 引き算をする際は逆の動作で行う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267416,
      "updated": 1775268186
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06e62000000000096c09c",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/cacb03f64babd33f79c3bb96de59a6cc]　　[https://gyazo.com/029620cb446bb1c599140f6dad5ad5fe]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267426,
      "updated": 1775267819
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06f6f000000000096c09e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267696,
      "updated": 1775267696
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06ebd000000000096c09d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267517,
      "updated": 1775267517
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06bf6000000000096c08d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775266807,
      "updated": 1775266807
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06ded000000000096c094",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267310,
      "updated": 1775267310
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06de9000000000096c093",
      "text": "[上添下排]:  足す際に一珠が足りない場合、五珠に繰り上げる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267306,
      "updated": 1775268239
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0721b000000000096c0a9",
      "text": "\t上にある五珠を添入し、下にある一珠を開排する。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268379,
      "updated": 1775268482
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06e0b000000000096c095",
      "text": " [$ 1=5 - 4]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267339,
      "updated": 1775268119
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06e37000000000096c097",
      "text": " [$ 2=5 - 3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267383,
      "updated": 1775268122
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06e38000000000096c098",
      "text": " [$ 3=5 - 2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267385,
      "updated": 1775268125
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06e38000000000096c099",
      "text": " [$ 4=5 - 1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775267385,
      "updated": 1775268133
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06536000000000096c070",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775265079,
      "updated": 1775265079
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07184000000000096c0a0",
      "text": "[下添上排]:  引く際に一珠が足りない場合、五珠を繰り下げる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268229,
      "updated": 1775268364
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07287000000000096c0aa",
      "text": "\t下にある一珠を添入し、上にある五珠を開排する。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268488,
      "updated": 1775268510
    },
    {
      "id": "69d071a3000000000096c0a7",
      "text": " [$ -1=-5 + 4]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268260,
      "updated": 1775268277
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07195000000000096c0a3",
      "text": " [$ -2=-5 + 3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268245,
      "updated": 1775268280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07195000000000096c0a4",
      "text": " [$ -3=-5 + 2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268245,
      "updated": 1775268282
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07195000000000096c0a5",
      "text": " [$ -4=-5 + 1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268245,
      "updated": 1775268284
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07195000000000096c0a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268245,
      "updated": 1775268245
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07185000000000096c0a1",
      "text": "[下排上進]:  足す際に五珠も一珠も足りない場合、上の位に繰り上げて、下の位から補数を引く。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268229,
      "updated": 1775268970
    },
    {
      "id": "69d073bc000000000096c0b7",
      "text": "\t[$ 1=10-5-4]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268797,
      "updated": 1775268964
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07301000000000096c0ac",
      "text": "\t[$ 2=10-5-3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268609,
      "updated": 1775268855
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0735f000000000096c0b0",
      "text": "\t[$ 3=10-5-2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268703,
      "updated": 1775268858
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0735f000000000096c0b1",
      "text": "\t[$ 4=10-5-1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268704,
      "updated": 1775268861
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0735b000000000096c0af",
      "text": "\t[$ 5=10-5]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268699,
      "updated": 1775268704
    },
    {
      "id": "69d071be000000000096c0a8",
      "text": "\t[$ 6=10-4]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268286,
      "updated": 1775268739
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07372000000000096c0b2",
      "text": "\t[$ 7=10-3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268722,
      "updated": 1775268741
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07373000000000096c0b3",
      "text": "\t[$ 8=10-2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268724,
      "updated": 1775268742
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07374000000000096c0b4",
      "text": "\t[$ 9=10-1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268724,
      "updated": 1775268743
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07375000000000096c0b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268725,
      "updated": 1775268794
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0739e000000000096c0b6",
      "text": "[上退下加]:  引く際に五珠も一珠も足りない場合、上の位から繰り下げて、下の位に補数を加える。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268767,
      "updated": 1775268988
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0741a000000000096c0b8",
      "text": "\t[$ -1=-10+5+4]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268891,
      "updated": 1775269052
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0741a000000000096c0ba",
      "text": "\t[$ -2=-10+5+3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268891,
      "updated": 1775269054
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0741a000000000096c0bb",
      "text": "\t[$ -3=-10+5+2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268891,
      "updated": 1775269057
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0741a000000000096c0bc",
      "text": "\t[$ -4=-10+5+1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268891,
      "updated": 1775269059
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0741a000000000096c0bd",
      "text": "\t[$ -5=-10+5]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268891,
      "updated": 1775269040
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0741a000000000096c0be",
      "text": "\t[$ -6=-10+4]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268891,
      "updated": 1775269044
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0741a000000000096c0bf",
      "text": "\t[$ -7=-10+3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268891,
      "updated": 1775269045
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0741a000000000096c0c0",
      "text": "\t[$ -8=-10+2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268891,
      "updated": 1775269047
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0741a000000000096c0c1",
      "text": "\t[$ -9=-10+1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775268891,
      "updated": 1775269049
    },
    {
      "id": "69d074ea000000000096c0c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775269098,
      "updated": 1775269098
    },
    {
      "id": "69d074f0000000000096c0c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775269104,
      "updated": 1775269104
    },
    {
      "id": "69d074f0000000000096c0c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775269105,
      "updated": 1775269105
    },
    {
      "id": "69d074c5000000000096c0c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775269061,
      "updated": 1775269061
    }
  ]
}